data.message: Stabilized enforcement means you can now compound CAPABILITY safely. The next phase is not "more rules" but "more capability guarded by minimal ruthless enforcement." The 5 next moves: (1) waiver protocol for controlled overrides, (2) network exfil/supply chain as next chokepoint, (3) explainable blocks that teach, (4) capability sprints with kill switches, (5) measure blocked incidents per week as the real signal.
